OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780304989
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Peter Mandelson
OL,4,Cpapers set to be published
OL,6,FThe documents could potentially reveal
OL,7,Fmore embarrassing and damaging details
OL,8,Fat a time when Sir Keir Starmer is
OL,9,Falready in a precarious position, as
OL,10,FITV News Political Correspondent
OL,11,FLouisa James explains.
OL,13,FHundreds of documents relating to the
OL,14,Fappointment of Lord Peter Mandelson as
OL,15,Fambassador to the US are expected to
OL,16,Fbe published on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
