FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780304989
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Peter Mandelson
OL,4,Cpapers set to be published
OL,6,FThe release, said to be the second
OL,7,Flargest publication to the House of
OL,8,FCommons in history, is the second
OL,9,Ftranche of documents on the peer's
OL,10,Fappointment.
OL,12,FMPs voted in February to demand
OL,13,Fministers publish a wide range of
OL,14,Fdocuments relating to the appointment
OL,15,Fusing an archaic parliamentary
OL,16,Fprocedure known as a "humble address".
OL,26,@xD@VOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780304989
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Peter Mandelson
OL,4,Cpapers set to be published
OL,6,FThe vote followed the launch of a
OL,7,Fpolice investigation into Lord
OL,8,FMandelson and concerns about the
OL,9,Fvetting process involved in his
OL,10,Fappointment.
OL,12,FA first tranche of documents, released
OL,13,Fin March, showed Sir Keir Starmer was
OL,14,Fwarned of a "general reputational
OL,15,Frisk" because of Lord Mandelson's
OL,16,Fconnection to the late paedophile
OL,17,Ffinancier Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,26,@vD@MOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780304989
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Peter Mandelson
OL,4,Cpapers set to be published
OL,6,FThe second set of documents is
OL,7,Fexpected to include messages between
OL,8,FLord Mandelson and ministers and
OL,9,Fgovernment advisers, including
OL,10,FStarmer's former chief of staff,
OL,11,FMorgan McSweeney.
OL,13,FFormer health secretary Wes Streeting
OL,14,Fhas already published his own messages
OL,15,Fwith Lord Mandelson, including a
OL,16,Fdiscussion of Gaza and criticisms of
OL,17,FSir Keir's leadership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780304989
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Peter Mandelson
OL,4,Cpapers set to be published
OL,6,FBut reports suggest it will not
OL,7,Finclude Lord Mandelson's UK Security
OL,8,FVetting (UKSV) summary after the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police asked the
OL,10,Fgovernment to withhold the document to
OL,11,Favoid jeopardising its investigation
OL,12,Finto alleged misconduct in public
OL,13,Foffice by the peer.
OL,15,FUKSV recommended against granting Lord
OL,16,FMandelson security clearance, but top
OL,17,FForeign Office official Sir Olly
OL,18,FRobbins overruled that advice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780304989
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Peter Mandelson
OL,4,Cpapers set to be published
OL,6,FSir Olly was effectively sacked in
OL,7,FApril after it emerged he had
OL,8,Foverruled the advice, with the prime
OL,9,Fminister insisting he was unaware of
OL,10,FUKSV's recommendation.
OL,12,FThe government has said it has only
OL,13,Fwithheld documents requested by the
OL,14,Fpolice, and all other documents will
OL,15,Fbe published.
OL,17,FSeveral documents have also been
OL,18,Fredacted, either to remove personal
OL,19,Fdetails such as the names of junior
OL,20,Fofficials or on national security
OL,21,Fgrounds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780304989
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Peter Mandelson
OL,4,Cpapers set to be published
OL,6,FRedactions on national security
OL,7,Fgrounds were agreed with Parliament's
OL,8,FIntelligence and Security Committee
OL,9,Ffollowing a compromise with MPs to
OL,10,Fhead off a backbench rebellion on the
OL,11,Fdemand for documents.
OL,13,FLast month, the committee raised
OL,14,Fconcerns that the government was
OL,15,Fapplying redactions "too broadly", and
OL,16,Fcited the UKSV vetting file as an
OL,17,Fexample of documents being withheld
OL,18,Fwithout Parliament granting ministers
OL,19,Fthe "authority" to do so.
OL,26,@wD@UOUwD@aO]{D@EOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
