OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780304989
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Peter Mandelson
OL,4,Cpapers set to be published
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe Conservatives have accused the
OL,12,Fgovernment of seeking to perpetrate a
OL,13,F"cover-up", with shadow minister Alex
OL,14,FBurghart writing to the chief
OL,15,Fsecretary to the Prime Minister on
OL,16,FSunday to demand "full transparency".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@JO]xD@ROUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780304989
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Peter Mandelson
OL,4,Cpapers set to be published
OL,6,FMr Burghart said: "I will remind you
OL,7,Fthat the House did not provide the
OL,8,Fgovernment with the choice about
OL,9,Fredactions beyond the narrow scope in
OL,10,Fthe humble address.
OL,12,F"This behaviour will be viewed by the
OL,13,FHouse as a contempt of Parliament, and
OL,14,Fas a cover-up by the British public.
OL,16,F"Even if the prime minister leaves
OL,17,Foffice in a few weeks, I can assure
OL,18,Fyou we will hold you to account for
OL,19,Fthis."
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780304989
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Peter Mandelson
OL,4,Cpapers set to be published
OL,6,FA government spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Fare committed to complying with the
OL,8,Fhumble address in full.
OL,10,F"The second tranche of documents will
OL,11,Fbe among the largest publications ever
OL,12,Flaid in Parliament.
OL,14,F"That reflects the transparent and
OL,15,Fthorough process we have followed, in
OL,16,Fline with established precedent for
OL,17,Fhumble addresses."
OL,26,@nD@aOUrD@AOUvD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
